D tameɣra n taddart.
Deg-s ma drus ɛecra n yicennayen ilmeẓyen n taddart-agi.
Kra n yicennayen n tudrin.
Gar yicennayen n taddart-agi i d-yecnan ad nebder Marseɣsan.
Acku argaz d netta i yettqabalen aεdaw n beṛṛa.
D argaz i yesεan tazmert n yifadden i tetteḥwiğ txeddimt n tmurt.
Takerza d tmegra.
Ɣef wayagi, dɣa, mi ara ilal uqcic ssiγritent tlawin.
Mi ara d-tlal d teqcict, berrun i wallen-nsen.
Mi terfed tmeṭṭut-is s tadist.
A tameṭṭut, ḥṣu tikkelt-agi ma d tallest i d-tesεiḍ, ad tt-nγeγ.
Ad gluγ s uqerru-m.
Muqel anida ara tegreḍ leεmeṛ-im.
Yewweḍ wass ideg ara terbu.
Iruḥ urgaz γer lexla am win yugaden.
Yeqqim s ddaw n tzemmurt.
A Ṛebbi ttxil-k kullec fell-ak yeshel.
Yegla ula s uxxam n jeddi-s.
Ad i yi-d-tmuddeḍ aya d waya neγ ad gluγ s leεmeṛ-ik.
Argaz, yeγli γef tgecrar.
Ad ak-ḥemmdeγ ad ak-cekkreγ d kečč i yeẓran d acu ideg yella leṣlaḥ.
Yella-d usarag wis sin n tdukkla-a.
Wwin-d awal s telqay deg temlilit-agi.
Amek teddes tmetti taqbaylit ?
Acu n unegmu i d-yellan deg-s ?
D tamɣart i d taxeznaǧit n uxxam.
D nettat i d-yelhan s yikufan.
Amɣar, yelha-d s tlufa n berra d trebga n warraw n warraw-is.
Zik d tajmeɛt n taddart i iferrun timsal.
Tizi n wass-a, tettwabeddel s teseqqamut n taddart.
Axeddim-is yegzem kan deg wakal n tɣiwant.
Mi ssulin awal-nsen, yella-d uskasi sɣur wid yellan deg tzeqqa-nni.
Yezzi wawal deg-s ɣef waṭas n temsal i d-yeqqnen ɣef usentel-a.
Anegmu n unagraw n tuddsa n tmetti taqbaylit taqburt.
Azwel n usarag-agi-nsen.
Ɣer taggara, ad d-nesmekti belli asarag aneggaru yettwajerd ɣef waṭṭan n ssker.
Ad yili umejjay Ɛmar Benassil d imsireg n temlilit-a.
Azekka n ttlata ad tili tmeɣra meqqren ara d-yilin i lfayda n yimeḍharen.
Jerden iman-nsen i wakken ad-zeynen.
S tallelt n Waggur azeggaɣ azzayri n tama-agi.
D tzeqqa n tmeɣriwin n Laɛzib Uheddad ara d-yesdurin tameɣra-a.
Ad tebdu tmeɣra-agi ɣef lɛecra d uzgen n yiḍ.
Ad d-ilin ddeqs n leqdicat idelsanen i lmend n yigerdan-a.
Gar wayen yettwaheggan deg wahil, ad d-nebder tuqna n lḥenni n yimeḍharen-agi.
Ccnawi d tbuɣarin sɣur timɣarin n tama-agi.
Afraq n wuraren i yigerdan-agi.
Yettuɛeggen diɣ ad yili usiher n yimseḍsi neɣ n useḥḥar ɣer tama n tmeɣra n ccna.
Ad d-ccnun kra n yilmeẓyen n tama-agi.
Ad d-ilint snat n tejmilin.
I lmend n waya, yella-d usileɣ n ugraw n yilmeẓyen deg tsellak timezwura.
Ad tili i uselway n teseqqamut n Waggur azeggaɣ azzayri n tama n At Ɛisa Mimun.
Aselmad mačči kan d win i d-yessegzayen timsirin.
Win ineǧǧṛen abrid n unelmad i yimal n lεali.
Daymi i as-fkan azal meqqṛen tmura n umaḍal.
Rran-t di rrif seg yal tama, ama seg tama n yizerfan, neɣ d tin n wazal.
D nutni i yesɣarayen, d nutni i d iεessasen n warrac.
D iqeddacen n tneččit.
Aneɣlaf n usegmi, yerra-d i usiwel-nsen s uɣiwel.
Yefra-asen yiwen n uɣbel i llan yakan sεan-t.
Azemz n yikayaden.
Aredmani, d inelmaden n tesnawit.
D wid uɣerbaz alemmas i ixeddmen ikayaden d imezwura.
D nutni daɣen i iteffɣen imuṛaṣ uqbel.
Ayagi yeffeɣ ɣef warrac, imi εyan mliḥ seg wahil yeččuṛen.
Yuɣal uqcic ur iteṭṭef ara, neɣ s unamek-nniḍen ẓẓay i tegzi.
Afennan Belxir Muḥend, yella yesmeḥsis i yicennayen iqburen am Sliman Ɛazem.
Deg-s sebɛa n tezlatin anda i d-yessefra s ccna.
Kra n yisental i yerzan timetti sumata.
Ulmud n uẓawan deg uxxam n yidles Mulud Mɛemmri n temdint n Tizi Uzzu.
Ad naf aṭas n tecraḍ-is deg tezlatin-agi timaynutin.
Iwala d akken ccna aqbayli yebda yettmili iteffeɣ i ubrid, sya ɣer da.
I wid yebɣan ad slen aẓawan aḥlawan n teqbaylit d yisefra zeddigen
Yezmer ad yessemḥes, ihi, i sebɛa n tezlatin-agi.
Yewwi-d ass-a amaynut-nniḍen.
Adlis-a n wurar s wawalen, i d-yeffɣen di teẓrigin n Ccix Muḥend Ulḥusin.
Deg wawal i d-newwi yid-s, negza belli leqdic-a, d axeddim n yiseggasen.
Uraren-a llan ffɣen-d yakan deg yisebtar n Uɣmis n Yimaziɣen.
Di taggara, Mhenni yerra-as tajmilt i weltma-s Kaysa.
ibudd-as adlis-a i yiziɣer-is.
Nettat i t-iεewnen aṭas deg leqdic-a.
Faṭma Caɛbi, d tanaẓurt, si zik-is tḥemmel ccna aqdim.
Tsell aṭas i radyu tis snat, ladɣa tidwilin-nni n ccna.
Seg wasmi tella meẓẓiyet, tḥemmel icennayen imeqqranen n teqbaylit.
Tettaɛraḍ ad tecnu i yiman-is deg uxxam.
Ulamma ɣef zik n lḥal i tebda ccna s ṣṣut-is ḥlawen.
Ur tgi ara isurifen ɣer sdat.
Tmugger-d imir ugur n tmetti, yettagin ad tecnu tmeṭṭut.
Tura akka, ha-tt-an la tettheggi i wakken ad tessufeɣ yiwen n album.
Am wakken daɣen i yetturaǧu, sya d afella, ad tessufeɣ tasfift i yiman-is.
Ɣer taggara, ad d-nesmekti kan belli, Faṭma Caɛbi tlul deg Lezzayer Tamaneɣ.
Armi tmeqqer i d-tuɣal ɣer tmurt-is tanaṣlit Rǧawna.
Aseggas-agi, iḥella-d kraḍ n cciεat n teẓruft deg tedwilt tn Talɣuɣa n ddunit.
Tella-d tedwilt-a deg waggur n yebrir.
Tarbaεt n tmurt n Lezzayer, tettekka stesɛa n yinaddalen.
Tḥella-d xemsin n cciεat yemgaraden.
Naɛman Nadir, d yiwen n yilemẓi i yesεan tmanya uɛecrin n yiseggasen.
Yezdeɣ deg taddart n At Zεim, yetabaεen ɣer tɣiwant n Mεatqa.
Iḥella-d deg umahil-is anaddal snat n cciεat n wuraɣ.
Rebεa n cciεat n teẓruft d Snat n cciεat n udrenz.
Yurar unaddal-a deg terbaεt n waddal amaswaḍ Idurar.
